HEADWORD: Vibroscope
<hw>Vi"bro*scope</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An
instrument for observing or tracing vibrations.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An instrument resembling the
phenakistoscope.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

